Detailed Description

cvmx_gmx::_rx::_stats_pkts_drp

Count of all packets received that were dropped due to a full receive FIFO. This counts both partial packets in which there was enough space in the RX FIFO to begin to buffer and the packet and total drops in which no packet was sent to PKI. This counts good and bad packets received - all packets dropped by the FIFO. It does not count packets dropped by the dmac or pause packet filters.
